    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "Generate a list of 50 real B2B business niches focused on contractors, trades, industrial services, building maintenance, construction suppliers, HVAC, electrical, plumbing, roofing, fabrication, or wholesale supply businesses that serve small and medium-sized businesses (SMEs), each in a different random country.\n\nYour response must be a strict JSON object containing an array of strings. Do not include markdown formatting and do not add any conversational text before or after the JSON.\n\nEach item must follow this exact format: \"City Business Type\"\n\nKeep each value short and simple, like a Google Maps search query (e.g. \"Dallas HVAC Contractor\"). Use only letters and spaces, STRICTLY no commas. Maximum 8 words per item.\n\nAvoid technology companies, software firms, IT services, marketing agencies, coworking spaces, startups, offices, and digital services.\n\nReturn exactly this structure:\n{\"items\":[\"Dallas HVAC Contractor\",\"Brisbane Roofing Supplier\",\"Johannesburg Electrical Contractor\"]}",
        "options": {}
      },
